title: Branislav Ľupták
text:
Branislav Ľupták (born 5 June 1991) is a <a href="Slovakia">Slovak</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> midfielder who currently plays for MFK Dukla Banská Bystrica, competing in <a href="2.%20Liga%20%28Slovakia%29">2. Liga</a>.
Career.
He made his debut for <a href="FK%20Dukla%20Bansk%C3%A1%20Bystrica">Dukla Banská Bystrica</a> against <a href="FC%20Nitra">Nitra</a> on 16 July 2011.
On 3 July 2019 Ľupták signed a contract with <a href="Romania">Romanian</a> <a href="Liga%20II">Liga II</a> side <a href="SCM%20Gloria%20Buz%C4%83u">Gloria Buzău</a>. He left the club after a single season.
